-- Bank Asya shares fall to record low amid uncertainity over its future
-- By Ayla Jean Yackley
-- Tue Sep 16, 2014 02:41AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, Sept 16 (Reuters) - Shares in Turkey's Bank Asya <ASYAB.IS> fell 10 percent to 89 kurus, a record low, at the stock market's opening on Tuesday amid uncertainty over its future.

